---
title: Carb Smart Roasted Buffalo Chicken with Dill Sour Cream Dipper and Roasted Veggies
description: Feel like chicken wings but don't feel like dealing with the clean-up of deep-frying? Say hello to baked chicken breasts doused in hot sauce!  We know that "wing night" isn't complete without a side sauce, so you'll whip up a satisfying dip made with sour cream, chives and dill. While the chicken roasts, you'll also roast zucchini, carrots and onions to serve on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-buffalo-roti-6b2bc66d.jpg
